author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Livzon Pharma plans industry fund, unit in alliance with Epirus Switzerland
text:
Sept 24 Livzon Pharmaceutical Group Inc
* Says unit Livzon Mabpharm signs collaboration agreement with Switzerland's Epirus Switzerland
* Says plans to set up industry fund worth 500 million yuan ($78.35 million) with partner
